data.description: Experience convenient living! This appealing 2-bed, 1.75-bath townhome in Greenwood Villas features a covered patio perfect for leisurely afternoons. The living room has vaulted ceilings and a mix of push carpet and tile flooring. The kitchen is equipped with granite counters, recessed panel cabinets, and built-in appliances. Relax after a long day in the cozy main bedroom, offering a walk-in closet and a private bathroom for added comfort. Enjoy access to the Community pool, a refreshing escape on warm days. Ideally located near parks, restaurants, and shopping. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
